One more thing I notice in your view DDL
In your earlier view SQL, you had:
SELECT DISTINCT ...QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (...) = 1
DISTINCT is usually unnecessary here. It may not be the cause, but for clean validation I would remove DISTINCT and rely only on QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER().
